name: Empty Bedroom? (The Entity)
description:
The empty bedroom has some visitors. Some time portals have opened. The Entity searches for something -- someone. The Entity is an AI from a future beyond the human apocalypse. More at https://bit.ly/sageAnomaly

This was created from an edited image from an artist Bembo Davis (https://twitter.com/BemboDavis) on Twitter who put green blobs on a Craigslist posting. See original Tweet (https://twitter.com/BemboDavis/status/1244811871535808512) This work is released under the my Remix License (https://bardionson.com/remixLicense1.html)
